    "On , your recovery, sleep, HRV and workouts are shared with the provider for tailored coaching.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "On , your recovery, sleep, HRV and workouts are shared with the provider for tailored coaching."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "An , deine Erholung, dein Schlaf, deine HRV und Workouts werden für maßgeschneidertes Coaching mit dem Anbieter geteilt."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Вкл. , ваше восстановление, сон, ВСР и тренировки передаются провайдеру для персональных рекомендаций."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Activé , votre récupération, sommeil, VFC et entraînements sont partagés avec le fournisseur pour un coaching personnalisé."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Activado: tu recuperación, sueño, VFC y entrenamientos se comparten con el proveedor para un asesoramiento personalizado."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "On, il tuo recupero, sonno, HRV e allenamenti vengono condivisi con il provider per un coaching su misura."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "On a 5/MG connection NOOP will send a puffin realtime-stream request after the handshake, and log what comes back. If you have a 5/MG strap, turning this on and sharing your strap log helps map the protocol. No effect on WHOOP 4.0.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "On a 5/MG connection NOOP will send a puffin realtime-stream request after the handshake, and log what comes back. If you have a 5/MG strap, turning this on and sharing your strap log helps map the protocol. No effect on WHOOP 4.0."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bei einer 5/MG-Verbindung sendet NOOP nach dem Handshake eine Puffin-Echtzeitstream-Anfrage und protokolliert die Antwort. Wenn du einen 5/MG-Strap hast, hilft das Aktivieren und Teilen deines Strap-Protokolls, das Protokoll zu kartieren. Keine Auswirkung auf WHOOP 4.0."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "При подключении к 5/MG NOOP после установления соединения отправит запрос на поток данных puffin в реальном времени и запишет полученный ответ. Если у вас браслет 5/MG, включение этой функции и отправка журнала браслета помогут разобраться в протоколе. На WHOOP 4.0 это не влияет."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sur une connexion 5/MG, NOOP enverra une requête de flux temps réel puffin après la poignée de main et journalisera ce qui revient. Si vous avez un bracelet 5/MG, activer ceci et partager votre journal de bracelet aide à cartographier le protocole. Aucun effet sur le WHOOP 4.0."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "En una conexión 5/MG, NOOP enviará una solicitud de transmisión en tiempo real «puffin» tras el handshake y registrará lo que reciba. Si tienes una correa 5/MG, activar esto y compartir el registro de tu correa ayuda a mapear el protocolo. No afecta a la WHOOP 4.0."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Con una connessione 5/MG, NOOP invierà una richiesta di flusso in tempo reale puffin dopo l'handshake e registrerà ciò che riceve. Se hai una fascia 5/MG, attivare questa opzione e condividere il registro della fascia aiuta a mappare il protocollo. Nessun effetto sulla WHOOP 4.0."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open-source BLE reverse-engineering work. Thank you.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Open-source BLE reverse-engineering work. Thank you."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
